repository.description:
## Overview

HMS-NFO (Specialty Knowledge) is a sophisticated data processing and transformation system that powers the DataLayer component of the CodifyHQ architecture. It processes specialized domain knowledge from various sources, cleans and transforms it, and prepares it for use by AI agents and other system components.

work_items.description: Add integration tests for HMS-NFO with HMS-ETL, HMS-ESR, HMS-DOC
